NUM_REALIZATIONS 10
MIN_REALIZATIONS 1

RANDOM_SEED 1234

GEN_KW COEFFS coeff_priors

INSTALL_JOB mock_sim2seis MOCK_SIM2SEIS
FORWARD_MODEL mock_sim2seis

